## Marked in browser

Rendered by **marked**.

The initialization code:

```js
marked.setOptions({{
   highlight: function (code) {{
      return hljs.highlightAuto(code).value;
   }}
}});
$('.md-content').each(function() {{
   var elem = $(this);
   elem.html(marked(elem.text()));
}});
```

